Text: Do I need to do anything special to install this? I just got my first gps and it only has USA. I want canada, too. Thank you.

This is an EXE file.  If it's not a virus, it looks like the update directly from Garmin's website and it could cause you problems in trying to install.  The unlock code is unique and you have to generate another. You need a MAP ID. Unfortunately, there isn't a good working version out now.  Try the one that includes Mexico instead. It's an IMG file: http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5211110/Garmin_City_Navigator_2010.30_USA_Mexico_Canada_IMG_Unlocked
